name: Prajakta Koli
text:
"Hi Kutri aaplya baddal Internet var lihite ahe." 
Translates to - 
"This bitch is writing about us on the internet."

name: Prajakta Koli
text:
It was an eventful day at the bank. 
I asked her to like and subscribe before I hugged her goodbye.

name: Prajakta Koli
text:
She replied in English. 
#Smooth

name: Prajakta Koli
text:
I asked her if she has a pen. 
In marathi.

name: Prajakta Koli
text:
She just whispered to her daughter, "Hi Kutri aaplya baddal Internet var lihite ahe."   
They think I don't speak marathi.

name: Prajakta Koli
text:
The lady behind me however laughed as I tweeted. 
She has been peeking into my phone the whole time.

name: Prajakta Koli
text:
The lady in front of me dropped her pen for the 7th time. 
And looked at me like I am the pen-bearer.
For the 7th time.
